==English==

===Adjective===
'''multiple'''

# Having more than one [[element]], [[part]], [[component]] or [[function]]
#: My Swiss Army knife has '''multiple''' blades

====Synonyms====
*[[manifold]]

===Noun===
'''multiple'''  (''plural:'' [[multiples]])

# {{cattag|Mathematics}}: A [[number]] that may be [[divide]]d by another number with no [[remainder]]; thus 14, 21 and 70 are '''multiples''' of 7

